{
  "stem": "3150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And his closest neighbor, I'm sure, was a half-- a quarter mile away or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you-- people, you know, they worked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you really-- all day long you didn't say a word.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of animals they stored, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, you probably had a half-a-dozen cows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how you survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think he had four horses, if I'm-- if I'm correct.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And really, a-- a lot of bread and a lot of kielbasa, salami, like, you know, a lot-- a lot-- a lot of that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kosher?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Including [YIDDISH], don't worry, there was that too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I really don't know how my-- how my mother or father did it, but they knew the Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- somehow they knew when it was, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't even really answer you how they knew, but they knew when it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When it was-- and we were there a whole-- all of 1943.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew when Pesach was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know that they did anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It didn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they knew, you know, it's Pesach, it's Shavuot, and it's the High Holiday.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somehow, they knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- before my mother-- my father died, he used to say-- he used to cry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to say, the only-- he used to look at me and say, he's the only guy who hasn't lived yet.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in fact, he was not-- he was already-- he died a year before I was bar mitzvahed So I was never bar mitzvahed, in fact.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was never bar mitzvahed for a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was not bar mitzvahed till-- till 1993.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Temple Torah.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
